  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Shooting in Kelaniya: One killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A man was killed and a woman and a two-year-old child were injured in a shooting at Pattiya Junction in Kelaniya today, police spokesman SSP Nihal Thalduwa said.",
        "The deceased has been identified as a 31 year old resident of Veyangoda.",
        "The victim was traveling on a motorbike with his wife and child when two unidentified persons on a motorbike opened fire on him, the spokesman said.",
        "The media spokesman said that the woman who was shot was a passerby",
        "It has not yet been revealed whether the deceased's wife was shot",
        "The injured child was admitted to the Lady Ridgeway Children's Hospital while the other injured woman was admitted to the Colombo National Hospital",
        "The body of the deceased has been placed at the Colombo National Hospital, the spokesman added"
      ],
